title: Ep - 30 - Laguna Beach's Jason Wahler & Heather McDonald
description:
Jason Wahler From Laguna Beach and The Hills explains how he overcame addiction, Kara Berry and Kate watch an episode of MTV's The Challenge, and Heather Mcdonald helps Kate dissect the premiere of Dancing With The Stars and this week's Real Housewives of Beverly Hills.
